urlText: Moore Park lift out of service
content:
The lift at Moore Park light rail stop (Anzac Parade side of the Dr Agnes Bennett footbridge) is out of service until further notice.

For your safety, do not use even if the doors open.

Alternative access:
  • Use the stairs if able to,
    Or use the accessible entry/exit pathway via the crossing at the intersection of Anzac Parade and Lang Road.
     
For urgent assistance:
  • Use the Help Point if on the platform
    Or call 131 500
subtitle: Moore Park lift out of service

properties.smsText: Moore Park lift out of service
properties.speechText: The lift at Moore Park light rail stop (Anzac Parade side of the Dr Agnes Bennett footbridge) Line is out of service until further notice. For your safety, do not use even if the doors open. Use the stairs if able to, or use the accessible entry/exit pathway via the crossing at the intersection of Anzac Parade and Lang Road. For urgent assistance, use the Help Point if on the platform or call 131 500.
